{"tid":936645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘繞道校巴撞欄　司機學童9人傷","createTime":"2018-12-11T02:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T03:17:00.000Z","uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b98f7a9a678b370dd1f5b7b525ab37187ec8d7b","tid":936645,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"今早(11日)7時42分，一輛校巴沿觀塘繞道往沙田方向行駛，至太子道東支路時，突然失事撞向分岔路口風琴式防撞欄，繼而衝前數米撞向壆，意外中，司機，保母及7名學童受傷被困，多輛消防車及救護車到場拯救，坍塌搜救專隊亦到場協助救出傷者，幸受傷學童傷勢輕微，救護員為他們檢查後送院。消息指，事發時校巴因閃避切線車失控，撞向風琴欄石壆被困，校巴負責接載馬鞍山一間國際學校外籍學童。 <br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，觀塘繞道往旺角方向通往太子道東支路的唯一行車線一度封閉。車龍曾塞至將軍澳隧道。 <br />\n<br />\n又黎一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ace8064326e63ea385059d46097ae6e865b6b0","tid":936645,"uid":14374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f741c44da22c7ba851e039f78933ff79138cd76a","tid":936645,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8621682cff27b69f6a15e7d87edff22be1c42161","tid":936645,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d0c276ade210ab2f9b374e5f9c6a4ad3db850","tid":936645,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"又校巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329b0a44f08a5e0b49792c2bfe8644220d88a4b6","tid":936645,"uid":10703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:07:16.000Z","msg":"坍塌搜救專隊連續出動左兩日<img src=\"/